Create TimelineGrid.tsx in src/renderer/src/componentes/. This is a NEW file and the largest subtask.

PROPS INTERFACE (TimelineGridProps):
- colaboradores: Colaborador[]
- alocacoes: Alocacao[]
- setor: Setor (for hora_abertura/hora_fechamento)
- dataSelecionada: string (YYYY-MM-DD format, the day to display)
- dataInicio: string (period start, for day navigation bounds)
- dataFim: string (period end, for day navigation bounds)
- demandas?: Demanda[]
- tiposContrato?: TipoContrato[]
- readOnly?: boolean (default false)
- onCelulaClick?: (colaboradorId: number, data: string, statusAtual: string) => void
- loadingCell?: { colaboradorId: number; data: string } | null
- changedCells?: Set<string> (default new Set())
- violatedCells?: Set<string> (default new Set())

IMPORTS:
- { useState, useMemo } from 'react'
- { ChevronLeft, ChevronRight } from 'lucide-react'
- { Button } from '@/components/ui/button'
- { Tooltip, TooltipContent, TooltipTrigger } from '@/components/ui/tooltip'
- { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge'
- { cn } from '@/lib/utils'
- { CORES_CONTRATO } from '@/lib/cores'
- { toMinutes, formatarMinutos, iniciais, formatarData } from '@/lib/formatadores'
- Types from '@shared/index': Alocacao, Colaborador, Setor, Demanda, TipoContrato

CORE LOGIC:

1. TIME SLOTS CALCULATION:
   - Calculate totalMinutes = toMinutes(setor.hora_fechamento) - toMinutes(setor.hora_abertura)
   - SLOT_SIZE = 30 (minutes per slot)
   - totalSlots = totalMinutes / SLOT_SIZE
   - Generate timeLabels array: for each hour from hora_abertura to hora_fechamento, push the hour string (e.g., '06:00', '07:00', ..., '22:00'). Only full hours, not every 30min slot.

2. DATA MAPS (useMemo):
   - alocacaoMap: Map<string, Alocacao[]> keyed by colaborador_id, filtered to dataSelecionada only. Group multiple alocacoes per colaborador on same day (for split shifts with interval). Key: string(colaborador_id). Value: Alocacao[] sorted by hora_inicio.
   - contratoMap: Map<number, TipoContrato> keyed by tipo_contrato_id (from tiposContrato prop)

3. COLABORADORES SORTED: useMemo to sort colaboradores by rank ascending.

4. DAY NAVIGATION:
   - State: dataSelecionada is a PROP but the parent controls it. However, we need internal navigation. Add onDateChange?: (date: string) => void to props. Or better: manage dataSelecionada internally with useState initialized from prop. Use buttons ChevronLeft/ChevronRight to go prev/next day. Clamp to dataInicio..dataFim range. Show formatted date and day-of-week name (e.g., 'Ter 01/03').
   - Actually, SIMPLIFY: use useState<string> for currentDate initialized from dataSelecionada prop. Navigation buttons adjust +/- 1 day. Show day name + date.

5. BAR POSITION CALCULATION:
   Helper function calcBarPosition(horaInicio: string, horaFim: string): { start: number; end: number }
   - startOffset = toMinutes(horaInicio) - toMinutes(setor.hora_abertura)
   - endOffset = toMinutes(horaFim) - toMinutes(setor.hora_abertura)
   - gridStart = Math.floor(startOffset / SLOT_SIZE) + 2  (col 1 is the sidebar)
   - gridEnd = Math.ceil(endOffset / SLOT_SIZE) + 2
   - return { start: gridStart, end: gridEnd }

6. COLOR LOOKUP:
   Helper function getBarColor(tipoContratoId: number): { bar: string; text: string; border: string }
   - Look up contratoMap.get(tipoContratoId)?.nome
   - Return CORES_CONTRATO[nome] || CORES_CONTRATO['DEFAULT']

RENDER STRUCTURE:

The component renders a scrollable container with CSS Grid:

```
<div className="space-y-3">
  {/* Day Navigation */}
  <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
    <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
      <Button variant="outline" size="icon" className="size-8" onClick={prevDay} disabled={atStart}>
        <ChevronLeft className="size-4" />
      </Button>
      <span className="text-sm font-medium min-w-[140px] text-center">
        {dayName} {formatarData(currentDate)}
      </span>
      <Button variant="outline" size="icon" className="size-8" onClick={nextDay} disabled={atEnd}>
        <ChevronRight className="size-4" />
      </Button>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Timeline Grid */}
  <div className="overflow-x-auto rounded-lg border">
    <div
      className="relative min-w-[800px]"
      style={{
        display: 'grid',
        gridTemplateColumns: `180px repeat(${totalSlots}, 1fr)`,
        gridTemplateRows: `auto repeat(${sortedColaboradores.length}, 48px) auto`,
      }}
    >
      {/* HEADER ROW */}
      {/* Sticky corner cell (row 1, col 1) */}
      <div className="sticky left-0 z-20 bg-muted/40 border-b border-r px-3 py-2 flex items-end">
        <span className="text-xs font-semibold text-foreground">Colaborador</span>
      </div>
      {/* Time labels - render one label per HOUR spanning 2 columns (2 x 30min slots) */}
      {timeLabels.map((label, i) => (
        <div
          key={label}
          className="border-b bg-muted/40 px-1 py-2 text-center text-[10px] font-medium text-muted-foreground"
          style={{ gridColumn: `${i * 2 + 2} / ${i * 2 + 4}` }}
        >
          {label}
        </div>
      ))}

      {/* COLLABORATOR ROWS */}
      {sortedColaboradores.map((colab, rowIndex) => {
        const allocsToday = alocacaoMap.get(String(colab.id)) || []
        const contrato = contratoMap.get(colab.tipo_contrato_id)
        const colors = getBarColor(colab.tipo_contrato_id)
        const isViolatedRow = violatedCells.has(`${colab.id}-${currentDate}`)
        const hasWork = allocsToday.some(a => a.status === 'TRABALHO')
        const isFolga = !hasWork && allocsToday.some(a => a.status === 'FOLGA')
        const isIndisponivel = allocsToday.some(a => a.status === 'INDISPONIVEL')
        const gridRow = rowIndex + 2  // row 1 is header

        return (
          <React.Fragment key={colab.id}>
            {/* Sidebar cell - sticky left */}
            <div
              className={cn(
                'sticky left-0 z-10 bg-background border-b border-r px-3 flex items-center gap-2',
                isViolatedRow && 'bg-destructive/5'
              )}
              style={{ gridRow, gridColumn: 1 }}
            >
              <div className={cn('flex size-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-[10px] font-semibold', colab.sexo === 'F' ? 'bg-pink-100 dark:bg-pink-950/30 text-pink-700 dark:text-pink-300' : 'bg-sky-100 dark:bg-sky-950/30 text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300')}>
                {iniciais(colab.nome)}
              </div>
              <div className="min-w-0">
                <div className="text-xs font-medium leading-tight text-foreground truncate">
                  {colab.nome.split(' ').slice(0, 2).join(' ')}
                </div>
                <div className="text-[10px] text-muted-foreground truncate">
                  {contrato?.nome ?? 'Contrato'}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* Background for the entire row (grid lines) */}
            <div
              className={cn('border-b col-span-full', isViolatedRow && 'bg-destructive/5')}
              style={{ gridRow, gridColumn: `2 / ${totalSlots + 2}` }}
            />

            {/* Shift bars OR status badges */}
            {hasWork && allocsToday.filter(a => a.status === 'TRABALHO' && a.hora_inicio && a.hora_fim).map((alloc, i) => {
              const pos = calcBarPosition(alloc.hora_inicio!, alloc.hora_fim!)
              return (
                <Tooltip key={i}>
                  <TooltipTrigger asChild>
                    <div
                      className={cn(
                        'flex items-center justify-center rounded-md mx-0.5 my-1 text-[10px] font-medium cursor-default',
                        colors.bar, colors.text, colors.border, 'border',
                        !readOnly && alloc.status !== 'INDISPONIVEL' && 'cursor-pointer hover:opacity-90',
                        changedCells.has(`${colab.id}-${currentDate}`) && 'ring-2 ring-primary ring-offset-1',
                        isViolatedRow && 'ring-2 ring-destructive',
                      )}
                      style={{ gridRow, gridColumn: `${pos.start} / ${pos.end}` }}
                      onClick={() => {
                        if (!readOnly && onCelulaClick) {
                          onCelulaClick(colab.id, currentDate, alloc.status)
                        }
                      }}
                    >
                      {alloc.hora_inicio} - {alloc.hora_fim}
                    </div>
                  </TooltipTrigger>
                  <TooltipContent side="top" className="text-xs space-y-1">
                    <p className="font-semibold">{colab.nome}</p>
                    <p>{contrato?.nome ?? 'Contrato'}</p>
                    <p>{alloc.hora_inicio} -> {alloc.hora_fim}</p>
                    {alloc.minutos && <p>Total: {formatarMinutos(alloc.minutos)}</p>}
                  </TooltipContent>
                </Tooltip>
              )
            })}

            {/* Intervals between work blocks: if 2+ work allocs, render translucent bars in the gaps */}
            {hasWork && (() => {
              const workAllocs = allocsToday.filter(a => a.status === 'TRABALHO' && a.hora_inicio && a.hora_fim).sort((a, b) => toMinutes(a.hora_inicio!) - toMinutes(b.hora_inicio!))
              const intervals = []
              for (let i = 0; i < workAllocs.length - 1; i++) {
                const gapStart = workAllocs[i].hora_fim!
                const gapEnd = workAllocs[i + 1].hora_inicio!
                if (toMinutes(gapEnd) > toMinutes(gapStart)) {
                  intervals.push({ start: gapStart, end: gapEnd })
                }
              }
              return intervals.map((gap, i) => {
                const pos = calcBarPosition(gap.start, gap.end)
                return (
                  <div
                    key={`gap-${i}`}
                    className="flex items-center justify-center rounded mx-0.5 my-1.5 text-[9px] text-muted-foreground bg-muted/40 dark:bg-muted/30 border border-dashed border-muted-foreground/20"
                    style={{ gridRow, gridColumn: `${pos.start} / ${pos.end}` }}
                  >
                    Intervalo
                  </div>
                )
              })
            })()}

            {/* FOLGA badge - centered in row */}
            {isFolga && !hasWork && (
              <div
                className="flex items-center justify-center my-1"
                style={{ gridRow, gridColumn: `2 / ${totalSlots + 2}` }}
              >
                <Badge variant="outline" className="text-[10px] text-muted-foreground">
                  FOLGA
                </Badge>
              </div>
            )}

            {/* INDISPONIVEL badge - centered with diagonal stripes background */}
            {isIndisponivel && (
              <div
                className="flex items-center justify-center my-1 rounded bg-amber-50/50 dark:bg-amber-950/20"
                style={{
                  gridRow,
                  gridColumn: `2 / ${totalSlots + 2}`,
                  backgroundImage: 'repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 4px, rgba(251,191,36,0.1) 4px, rgba(251,191,36,0.1) 8px)',
                }}
              >
                <Badge variant="outline" className="text-[10px] text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300 border-amber-300 dark:border-amber-700">
                  AUS.
                </Badge>
              </div>
            )}
          </React.Fragment>
        )
      })}

      {/* COVERAGE ROW (if demandas exist) */}
      {demandas && demandas.length > 0 && (() => {
        // Calculate coverage per 30min slot
        const coverageRow = gridRow after last collaborator
        // For each slot, count how many colaboradores have TRABALHO status
        // where their hora_inicio <= slotStart AND hora_fim > slotStart
        // Compare with max(demanda.min_pessoas) for matching time range
        // Render colored cells: green if coverage >= needed, amber/red if not
        // ... (see detailed description below)
      })()}
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Legend */}
  <div className="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-[10px] text-muted-foreground">
    {/* Render a swatch for each CORES_CONTRATO entry + FOLGA + INDISPONIVEL */}
  </div>
</div>
```

COVERAGE ROW DETAIL:
- Grid row index = sortedColaboradores.length + 2
- Sidebar cell: 'COBERTURA' label, sticky left, bg-muted/30
- For each 30min slot (index 0 to totalSlots-1):
  - slotStartMin = toMinutes(setor.hora_abertura) + slotIndex * 30
  - Count colaboradores where any TRABALHO alocacao has toMinutes(hora_inicio) <= slotStartMin AND toMinutes(hora_fim) > slotStartMin
  - Find max min_pessoas from demandas where the slot falls within demanda.hora_inicio..hora_fim range AND dia_semana matches or is null
  - Render cell at gridColumn: slotIndex + 2 / slotIndex + 3
  - Color: emerald if count >= needed, amber if count < needed
  - Show count as text

LEGEND:
- One swatch per contract type color (from CORES_CONTRATO) with contract name
- Interval swatch (dashed border muted)
- FOLGA swatch
- INDISPONIVEL swatch

DARK MODE:
- All colors MUST use dark: variants
- Background: bg-background for sidebar, bg-muted/40 for header
- Grid lines: border-b with default border color
- Bars: CORES_CONTRATO already has dark: variants

